    "Model development and parameter estimationThe first step in TDT model development is patient data acquisition.",
    "As mentioned in the above section, a range of multimodal and multi-scale data is needed to generate the first models.",
    "Since our TDT engine is a PBPRK model, the main data are those which impact radiopharmacokinetic.",
